// Dialog - StealTheGold 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2039068170" "<color orange>You pry open the Council crate and see your face reflected in a stack of shiny gold bricks!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3765302005" "Gleefully examine your fortune in gold"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3863994945" "<color orange> You don't know how long you knelt there, starring at the fortune in gold, but you are broken out of your reverie by the commotion of a sudden battle erupting elsewhere in the Council base. It looks like you aren't the only one here for the big pay day.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1180544569" "Take as much as you can carry"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Overdrive 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2707568492" "I don't know if I buy it, {HeroName}. The only way you could have gotten into this Council base is with Hollow Point and the 5th Column's help..."
// Answer Text :
"P8592459" "I wouldn't be caught dead working for that nutcase!"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2070346832" "No need to take things to the extreme. If you weren't working for them, then who are you working for?"
// Answer Text :
"P1315778533" "I'm not working for anyone."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P492986443" "Ah ha! I get it. You're betraying the 5th Column, but ran into trouble with the Council... wait... hrmmm. It's starting to sound like your story is checking out, {HeroName}. My men just found Hollow Point, Vulfgar, and Metzger, as well as a bunch of very irrate Council soldiers, and they're all cursing your name."
// Answer Text :
"P1101372572" "I told you, I'm a good guy, see..."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P974415442" "I'm surprised, {HeroName}. I didn't think a scoundrel could change {Hero.gender=male his|her} colors. But it looks like you took the initiative to try and set things right. I guess there is such a thing as honor amongst thieves.<br><br>Well, it looks like the Council split the gold up when they moved it, some of it appears to be missing. It looks like Longbow will be on this case for a bit longer. You should help us track it down."
// Answer Text :
"P3544160824" "Hiding your gold. "I caught a lucky break. Maybe next time.""

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1708967993" "Word off the street is that the Council was behind that theft of gold from the national treasury. Word also has it that they're storing the stash in a hidden Council base that isn't so hidden from a person with as many connections as you have. The gold is insured by the treasury, and as good as gone, so you'd be doing everyone a favor by liberating it from the Council. And if no one is the wiser, then what harm would it be if you were to go ahead and keep it? After all, you aren't trying to take over the world, just enjoy it."
// AcceptString :
"P533688425" "Steal the stolen gold from those dirty Council thieves."
// SendOffString :
"P2116771377" "Bashing your way into a Council base will earn you a few brownie points amongst the tighty whitey heroes of Paragon City. Plus, the Council will never admit that their stolen goods were stolen rightou out from under their noses. This plan is so perfect that you can't imagine anything going wrong."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2699240289" "Liberate gold from the Council"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1289212177" "The information you have about that hidden Council base won't stay secret for much longer. You'd better hit that Council base and steal the gold before they move it or someone else beats you to the punch. Who'd have thunk that being a hero would be such a heavy burden."
// TaskTitle :
"P2196017064" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Innocuous Slip of Paper</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
