// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - ElenaWalker 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P262647444" "{HeroName}?  Wait, you're not with these goons?"
// Answer Text :
"P882868048" "No, I'm here to free you."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1899138718" "So, it's true what they say about you.  You've turned over a new leaf, how does that make you feel?"
// Answer Text :
"P1102434011" "Spare me the psycho-babble, here's the thing.  My services aren't free."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2724921759" "What?  You want to charge me?  People really never do change.  Well I have some bad news for you then {HeroName}."
// Answer Text :
"P1575157907" "There's bad news?  Why is there always bad news?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P879526580" "This is the second time I've been robbed in the past week by The Looter and his cronies.  I guess the Freakshow thought the first robbery was so fruitful they'd just rob me a second time.  However, they were quite angry when they realized I had very little left after the first robbery.  If there's anything of value remaining, the Freakshow boss <color red>The Looter</color> has it."
// Answer Text :
"P3373383333" "Well, that's just great."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1967240012" "Please. {HeroName}, you've got to help me.  She'll kill me.  It's only a matter of time until Shock Treatment shows up.  She has this a horrible grudge against doctors.  Please, I am begging you."
// Answer Text :
"P2633321396" "... (continue)"
// Page InformationPage5 Text :
"P1164289181" "Look, I can't pay you.  I can see that you want to do good.  When I look into your eyes I can see that within you.  Now's your chance to do something good, truly altruistic.  In a matter of moments Shock Treatment will arrive and if you don't intervene, she'll kill me.  Could you live with yourself if that happened?"
// Page InformationPage6 Text :
"P3188869150" "{HeroName}, she's a killer.  She hates doctors, it has something to do with her past.  Rumor has it that a sick scientist tested the limits of human sanity through inflicting untold pain with elec--"
// Answer Text :
"P3329719618" "Fine, I'll help you, but spare me the history lesson alright?"
// Page InformationPage7 Text :
"P3455400932" "Thank you {HeroName}.  Thank you!  I'll make sure Paragon recognizes you for the hero that you are."
// Answer Text :
"P2391055356" "...ugh, this just keeps getting better and better."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
