"P1312803384" "A nobel prize winning doctor, who was likely wealthy before the award, likely has quite a bit of financial resources.  Rescuing her could be your biggest payday yet.  That and it won't make you look all soft to your connections in the Isles.  Sounds like a golden opportunity."
// AcceptString :
"P3197228306" "HERO: Liberate Dr. Walker and some of her excess cash!"
