// Clue Name :
"P2246951009" "A very thankful Frostfire"
// DetailString :
"P3742059182" "'{HeroName}, your timing couldn't be better.  I was jumped by these ex-council goons and then injected with some sort of neuro-toxin.  I'm not exactly sure what they're up to.  I know that there are others that were taken.  Find them {HeroName}!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RescuedMissThystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1178050893" "Miss Thystle held captive"
// DetailString :
"P753363133" "Before leaving, and emphatically thanking you for your help, Miss Thystle informed you of Hollow Point's plan to construct a weapon capable of permanently suppressing a super powered being's special abilities.  Shee seemed to think the weapon wasn't quite ready."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P653594094" "After some investigation, you're pretty sure you've uncovered exactly where Hollow Point has been hiding out.  Judging by the trail of bullet casings leading back to this warehouse he was being pursued by another force.  That means there might be someone other than Hollow Point and his ex-council cronies inside."
// AcceptString :
"P2482124411" "HERO: Procure Hollow Point's weapon stash"
// SendOffString :
"P2546563367" "There might be some competition for the advanced weaponry inside that warehouse.  You'd better hurry before someone catches you in there.  Afterall, as long as Hollow Point has those weapons Paragon and its heroes are in terrible danger."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3012779911" "Obtain Hollow Point's Weapons"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3130404041" "Time is of the essence.  It's best to get to the warehouse and procure those weapons before Hollow Point has a chance to use them."
// TaskTitle :
"P2222479819" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Disabled Shield Generator</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P666175868" "There's a lot of activity in here.  A lot more than you had anticipated.  You can hear muffled moans coming from ahead."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3834773371" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Disabled Shield Generator</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You stopped Hollow Point's plot of kidnapping a number of Paragon City's heroes and draining their power.  The weapons you procured while in Hollow Point's base of operations were too dangerous to risk them falling into the wrong hands.  You had the unfortunate task of destroying them.  This hero business is less profitable than you had hoped."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2705644942" "...too many of them."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3288643520" "{HeroName}!  You've...<em>Got to stop Hollow Point."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3719729067" "<em><em>He's got Frostfire, Miss Thystle and Blast Furnace.<em>He's...going to drain their powers."

