// RandomFameString :
"P542606590" "What's {HeroName} playing at?  I heard that they rescued Blast Furnace, Frostfire and Miss Thystle from some ex-council goons.  Isn't {HeroName} supposed to be a villain?  I'm confused."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL6-7_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - MaxwellGreenDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3099161417" "So, what's this all about?  I'm terribly sorry about my bodyguards attacking you, but you see a number of organizations want me dead.  You're the third uninvited guest I've had this week."
// Answer Text :
"P1811602082" "I'm here to find out who this 'J' character is and why he wants you dead."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3973295886" "Look, I'm just a programmer.  Err--well a very <b>wealthy</b> programmer.  You see I work for various organizations and develop encrypting software for them."
// Answer Text :
"P1562942589" "Get to the point Maxwell."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1181820868" "R-right, okay.  Well, recently I've been working with Crey Technologies.  In the process of developing new encryption software for them I accidentally discovered a master decrypter that will break through any encryption used by some...less savory organizations."
// Answer Text :
"P2255848440" "...let me guess, Arachnos."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P4234785169" "Yeah, and Nemesis and..well the list goes on."
// Answer Text :
"P86374305" "Is there any truth to you gathering data on ex-villains leaving the Rogue Isles?"
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1893973430" "Data on ex-villains?  No.  No, I just build encryption software.  Look, please protect me.  I'll give you anything."
// Answer Text :
"P341136180" "I'll tell you what.  My work will be free, but if I find out you're lying to me..."
// Page InformationPage5 Text :
"P1979494613" "Right, yeah.  Okay.  I get the picture.  Have a look around if you want, you'll find that I'm telling the truth."
// Answer Text :
"P515170056" "I'll do that."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - ArbiterJacobsDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P472178060" "Ah, uh..."
// Answer Text :
"P2793661434" "So, I assume you must be 'J'."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2067771411" "Y-yes.  I am Arbiter Jacobs!  I am the the living will of Lord Recluse!  Stand aside fool, or...err, I will be forced to <b>CRUSH</b> y--"
// Answer Text :
"P3437568446" "(Punch Arbiter Jacobs in the gut)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P191944724" "*cough*<br><br>*gasp*<br><br>*wheeze*"
// Answer Text :
"P1741959365" "You tried to set me up Jacobs.  I don't like being set up."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2442635936" "*gasp*<br><br>S-so, what happens now?"
// Answer Text :
"P2143862190" "We're done here.  You leave Maxwell alone and I won't tear your face off.  Deal?"
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P2230271539" "*cough*<br><br>It appears I don't have any other option.  Deal."
// Answer Text :
"P3161500821" "Good.  Get lost."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - EvidenceClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2436396332" "Threatening e-mails"
// DetailString :
"P1026132765" "You go through Maxwell's files and find that he has indeed developed a 'super decrypter'.  He has also received numerous death threats from a person who only identifies themselves as 'J'.  It appears that this 'J' character is a a high ranking Arachnos agent, possibly even an Arbiter.  He demands that the encrypter be handed over he will personally hand Maxwell over to Lord Recluse himself.  Maxwell was telling the truth.  You've got to help him."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P645338352" "You're pretty sure this Maxwell Green fellow has angered some big organization like Crey, Arachnos or the Family and wants to use you to get rid of him.  You can make sure Mr. Green is on the up and up and show this 'J' what happens to those that try to play tricks on you."
// AcceptString :
"P3303830492" "HERO: Find out what J is up to."
// SendOffString :
"P804243813" "You've seen this a dozen times before: Organization hires assassin to take out a supposedly bad person, bad person turns out to be good person, assassin rejects the job, and then organization frames assassin by killing the mark.  Well, that's not going to happen to you."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P680759132" "Find out what J is up to"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1511922925" "You're sick and tired of organizations like the Family, Crey and Arachnos taking advantage of people like yourself.  You're no fool and it's time to show them that."
// TaskTitle :
"P4094653339" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Oldest One in the Books</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2088532039" "This is the place.  Now to find out if there's any truth to J's claim.  He'll likely be in the back of the office, you should start searching for him there."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P242531539" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Oldest One in the Book</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Your instincts were correct once again.  This 'J' fellow turned out to be a man called Jacobs and somehow obtained the lofty title of Arbiter.  Jacobs wanted to frame you for Maxwell Green's murder and steal his decrypter software.  You made Jacobs look like a fool and saved Maxwell from being assassinated."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2661035696" "Find Green!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P929116621" "<em>For Arbiter Jacobs!<em>For Lord Recluse!"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3132798663" "Speak with Maxwell Green"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1865561571" "Speak with Arbiter Jacobs"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P524028227" "Maxwell Green"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1384001688" "Okay, so you all understand.  I don't care who it is, if they enter through that door...<em>Shoot them.  Just shoot.<em>Questions can be asked later."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2598185233" "<em>Wait!  Wait!  It's {HeroName}!<em>Hold your fire!<em>Stop shooting you idiots!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4092015091" "Sorry about that {HeroName}.  Don't worry, my bodyguards have the very best insurance.  They'll be fine.  What's that you have some questions for me?"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P2121783154" "Maxwell's Bodyguard"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2950375860" "<em><em>Roger!  Ready to rock."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1310948132" "<em>Eat lead!  AAHHHHHHH!!!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1505307808" "<em><em>Got it.  Just shoot."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3249335386" "{HeroName}!  Shoot!  SHOOOT!<em><em>What's that boss?<em>I can't hear you over all of the gun fire."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2795872957" "I'll uh...just hang here then."

