// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - OverDriveDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3285592727" "So it was you that Arachnos called in to execute me.  I thought you were considering to fight for good instead of your previous selfish mot--"
// Answer Text :
"P2178017418" "Give it a rest, I'm not going to kill you."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P302694701" "Well, I am pleasantly surprised."
// Answer Text :
"P1731313483" "Let's fight our way out of here Overdrive."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2756907918" "I'm afraid I won't be of much use in a fight.  They've drugged me.  I can hardly see straight and it's difficult to operate my suit's targeting systems and combat functions.  I'll need you to walk me out of here."
// Answer Text :
"P1044320421" "Not a problem, let's go.  I think these Arachnos goons are catching on."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3056788034" "<color orange>The air begins to crackle with energy and Overdrive begins to disappear</color><br><br>Wh-what's going on?  {HeroName}!  Hel--"
// Answer Text :
"P3898852440" "Uh oh, that's not good."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - MangleDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1683694181" "{HeroName}, I always knew you were a pathetic do-gooder.  The price of your failure will be extreme.  Not only will I release this footage of your brutality to the people of Paragon City, I will also kill Overdrive myself as well as make sure Arachnos hunts you down."
// Answer Text :
"P1537441239" "What makes you think I'm going to let you get away with this?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P106560928" "What makes you think you can stop me?"
// Answer Text :
"P4271151008" "(Punch Mangle in the teeth)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2326724680" "<color orange>Your fist passes through Mangle's partially incorporeal form as he begins to teleport away.</color><br><br>Ah ha haha!"
// Answer Text :
"P2613454818" "...(continue)"

