"P271677701" "In the middle of Overdrive thanking you, she was teleported away.  You're pretty sure it wasn't Paragon City's medi-porter too."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - MangleClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P67801209" "Mangle teleports away!"
// DetailString :
"P2896096501" "After handily defeating Mangle's Arachnos guards, he informs  you that he has Overdrive and is going to execute her himself somewhere in these caves.  Time is of the essence, you must save her."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2748070610" "Some people might see a problem, you see an opportunity.  Hopefully there's a way to both profit and not make too many enemies.  You definitely won't go back to the Rogue Isles unless it's on your own terms, and you certainly won't cooperate with Mangle or any Arachnos goons.  It's probably best to investigate and then go from there."
// AcceptString :
"P1360189931" "HERO: Investigate Arachnos Summons"
// SendOffString :
"P741125255" "You wonder who Arachnos expects you to execute.  Could it be someone big like  Positron, Penelope Yin or the like?  That'd be tempting, those big shots always seem to take all the glory.  Well, you're ready for whatever Arachnos or Mangle might throw at you.  You head off for the coordinates mentioned in the summons notice."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1662723484" "Investigate Summons"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P306243815" "Mangle isn't a patient person.  It's best to get over to the coordinates listed in this summons and to find out what this whole thing is about."
// TaskTitle :
"P3020360278" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Arachnos Summons Notice</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3128130871" "You can hear the clattering of heavily armored Arachnos agents echoing through these halls and off in the distance you can hear the muffled moans of someone in pain."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1604468061" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Arachnos Summons Notice</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You showed Arachnos and Mangle that you're not going back to the Rogue Isles unless it's on your terms.   Additionally you managed to destroy Mangle's footage of your exploits in the Rogue Isles and you managed to save a Paragon hero to boot.  Not bad.  Not bad at all."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1310487726" "Talk to Overdrive"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1302918498" "Talk to Mangle"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4119295293" "<em>...so this is it.<em>You're just going to kill me?"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
