"P2085182762" "{HeroName}.<em>You've arrived.<em>Complete your task and return with us and your --<em t=3>Wait... You have not intention of --"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2771921704" "How DARE YOU decline Lord Recluse's generous offer!<em>I'll make you suffer for your insolence!"
