// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL6-7_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BlastFurnaceDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P800115729" "Heh.  Sorry about that.  I guess I didn't get the memo of you being a good guy, or at least less of a bad guy.  Either that or I just felt like setting you on fire a little bit."
// Answer Text :
"P3092605177" "We can finish our little fight if you want."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P616571407" "I'll take a raincheck on that {HeroName}.  The important thing is that we find Flambeaux.  You see, I've taken her under my wing.  I thought I could bring a little bit of stability into her life."
// Answer Text :
"P2141846910" "Stability?  You thought tha--you know what?  Nevermind.  Let's just do this."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P696094815" "Alright, but hang on.  There's something important.  She got wind of the Rikti building some sort of device in here that would be really bad news if it were to be activated.  When we last talked it sounded really urgent.  That's when she ran off all crazy-like.  So, let's prioritize here.  Find this device and then Flambeaux, alright?"
// Answer Text :
"P3230183494" "What about you?  You're not going with me?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3989383788" "I'm going to scout around and see if I can't find her on my own.  It'll look bad if it seems like I needed your help."
// Answer Text :
"P3121795366" "Alright, fine...whatever."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - FlambeauxDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2019282537" "{HeroName}?  I totally had this!  You had to come in and ruin my fun.  I was...just tricking the Rikti into thinking they had bested me.  You see, then I was going to explode into actio--"
// Answer Text :
"P2116218819" "Enough!  If you keep pulling stunts like this people are going to get killed Flambeaux."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P84003829" "You came all the way down here just to yell at me?"
// Answer Text :
"P2383698081" "Yeah, pretty much.  Next time I may not be there to save your behind.  Keep that in mind."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RiktiDeviceClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1459457904" "Rikti Genetic Destabilizer"
// DetailString :
"P1837057665" "This strange device is supposedly capable of rapidly transforming humans into Rikti within a several mile radius.  Immediately after deactivating the destabilizer, you hear a piercing alarm ring through the halls of the Rikti base."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3899997853" "Flambeaux is going to get herself killed.  She has a tendency to rush off and put herself and others in mortal danger.  Her inability to think before acting is likely to also get others killed.  You could rescue her and hammer some sense into her empty head."
// AcceptString :
"P2123342203" "HERO: Track down Flambeaux"
// SendOffString :
"P474220262" "You plan on what you'll say to Flambeaux when you finally find her.  It won't be pretty.  That stupid kid is going to end up causing more trouble than she can handle."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3345519135" "Find Flambeaux"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3335698162" "Flambeaux is still in danger.  You'd better go find out where she's been taken before her assailants do something extreme."
// TaskTitle :
"P1407910220" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Torn Flame Print Fabric</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1634295856" "Rikti.  They're like cockroaches, they're in every little dark corner of this city."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P223206065" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Torn Flame Print Fabric</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You gave Flambeaux a stern talking to and also thwarted Tal'Bok's plan to turn the people of Paragon City into Rikti.  You're pretty sure your little chat made Flambeaux pretty angry.  She ran off like a petulant child after you yelled at her."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3199478393" "Talk to Blast Furnace"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P2280658367" "Survive Rikti Ambushes"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3295184698" "Give Flambeaux a stern talking to"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3401619512" "Flambeaux?<em>Flambeaux!<em>FLAMBEAUX!?<em>Where is that idiot girl?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3782888676" "{HeroName}!<em> You're behind her disappearance.<em>I should have known."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P195981993" "What?  You're looking for Flambeaux too?<em>Okay.<em>Truce.<em>We clearly want the same thing."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P845139914" "Oh crud.  I forgot to ask {HeroName} where {Hero.gender=Male he|she} was keeping Flambeaux."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3195594946" "Alright.  Let's work this out."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P732723753" "See ya around {HeroName}."

