// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL6-7_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - StarDuskDialog 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2392969113" "{HeroName}?  Why are you helping me?  So, the rumors about you are true.  Hah!  I never thought I would see the day."
// Answer Text :
"P1424712348" "What rumors?  What are you talking about?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3783057589" "Oh, you know.  That you've gone all 'boy scout' on us.  I've heard that you've quite regularly been working with the heroes of Paragon City."
// Answer Text :
"P1565662515" "Some of us want to make a difference while still making a profit.  Ever think about that?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1952638760" "It's impossible.  You can't do good and benefit.  You can't be both altruistic and selfish.  It doesn't work that way.  So, I just don't bother being altruistic.  Anyhow, how about untying these bonds and I'll give you the lowdown of what's going on here."
// Answer Text :
"P2655220251" "(Untie Stardusks binds)"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2482475291" "Ahhh, much better.  Ol' Nemesis has got himself a secret little automaton storage facility in here.  They made a couple automatons of myself.  The first one was defective.  The second one should be arriving anytime now."
// Answer Text :
"P2978488866" "I wouldn't count on it.  The Nemesis goons dropped the crate."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P3106813953" "Dropped it?  Again?  That's how the first one got broken.  Anyhow, they've got automaton copies of a bunch of different hero copies here.  What do you say we bust them up and make Nemesis look like a chump?"
// Answer Text :
"P2128315791" "Sounds like a plan.  Let's go."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DesdemonaClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3954515564" "Broken Desdemona Automaton"
// DetailString :
"P599162995" "This crate contains an automaton with a striking resemblence to Desdemona a demon summoning ex-villain!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - StarduskClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3743695364" "Empty Crate"
// DetailString :
"P3194660728" "This crate contains some broken bits of plastic and fabric that look like parts from Stardusk's costume."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - HeroClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// DetailString :
"P2698584197" "This crate only contains a very small piece of material that looks like it came from your costume."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P671877738" "If Nemesis programs these Rogue Isles refugees to perform acts of evil, it will give your kind a bad name.  Afterall, you and Stardusk are just trying to look after yourselves.  Plus, there might be some valuable technology stored within the...sewers.  Okay, maybe not, but you can't let Nemesis get away with this.  Plus, it never hurts to make friends amongst the heroes of Paragon."
// AcceptString :
"P2130474142" "HERO: Stop Nemesis Plot!"
// SendOffString :
"P2961358092" "You follow the directions on the note you found in the crate and easily locate the sewer entrance and coordinates.  This has got to be stopped before it gets out of hand."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2388002454" "Stop Nemesis Plot"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3340053708" "It's only a matter of time before these automatons are calibrated and hit the streets.  You better hit the sewers fast!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3548195522" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Familiar Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2038660663" "Just when you were thinking 'It's quiet...too quiet...' A loud crash of splintering wood is heard off in the distance.  These Nemesis soldiers really have butter fingers don't they?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3199171637" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Familiar Face</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>That was a lot more than you signed up for.  Evidently Nemesis had another copy of the Stardusk automaton in the hopper, but it appeared defective.  However, most importantly they had an automaton fashioned after you.  You couldn't let that hit the streets of Paragon."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P2514288970" "Speak with Stardusk"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P2504070779" "Stardusk"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1700011946" "Let me go you creeps or I'll melt your face!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P359284886" "Well lookie who we have here."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P2180879500" "...interesting."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_NAME :
"P538540460" "Nemesis Automaton"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3180960723" "<em><em>That's what she said...<em>That's what she said..."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P747691726" "<em>That's what she said..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2579563041" "Warhulk"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2875728720" "Where are those idiots?<em>They left me down here with these robotic cretins.<em>Oh give it a rest, you're doing it wrong."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1340366267" "Attack them you mindless morons!<em>Ugh, somebody just shoot me."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1246837703" "Ah haha, now this will be fun!<em>Let's find those other automatons and shut 'em down."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3084334263" "Desdemona, eh?  How do you make an automaton summon demons?<em>Do you suppose the demons are automatons as well?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P447276473" "This is the crate that contained my first copy.  Where is it now?"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P946019832" "...<em>That looks familiar.<em>Uh oh.  Incoming!"

