"P12757790" "{Hero.gender=male Dude, you are like, the most awesome ever! We should totally hang out. We could get matching sports cars, I could buy you a yacht. Oh! dude, do you need like a secret lair? Because I could totally buy you one of those and then we could like, hang out there and get all the ladies! Bro high-five!|I... I think I'm in love. Seriously, I'm going to inherit a fortune, we should totally get married... Like tomorrow. I'm serious.}"
