// Page Intro Text :
"P1101682438" "{Hero.gender=male I don't think I've ever seen a man quite like you before. Not afraid to get his hands dirty. Powerful, decisive. Take me with you.|You. Have. Got. To teach me how to do that! That was freaking awesome! We should totally hang out. We'd be unstoppable. I'd be the pretty rich girl, and you can be my creep bashing side kick. What do you say?}"
// Answer Text :
"P1063475517" "I have something better in mind..."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1877391686" "{Hero.gender=male Oh do you? Hmmmm, you have my attention.|<i>You</i> have a better idea? Pffft, that isn't your job. <i>Your</i> job is to make sure I get to do what I want, and I want you to be my creep bashing sidekick!}"
// Answer Text :
"P527773077" "Right, let's just get out of here first..."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3863578460" "Wait... I overheard them talking about a safe full of cash and valuables. I want to go see what's in there. I mean, it's not like these punks are gonna be able to use it in prison, right?"
// Answer Text :
"P4260782894" "You know, I'm starting to like the way you think..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - BlastFurnace 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2072644138" "I'm taking a big risk giving you a chance to explain yourself, {HeroName}. But I notice that the lady and her kids aren't tied up. What's going on?"
// Answer Text :
"P2943121190" "I rescued them you idiot!"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3083446128" "<color orange>Though you can't see his face under his helmet, you imagine that Blast Furnace is refraining from lashing out at your response. His response isn't what you expected.</color><br><br>It looks like you're the hero today, {HeroName}. Doesn't it feel good doing good deeds without alternate motives? I'm sure their thanks will be payment enough for all of us today.""
// Answer Text :
"P325384483" "What? Thanks as payment? Why you..."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3843875741" "Ah ah ah... Listen, {HeroName}, just try the high road for once, I think you'll come to enjoy it. Besides, do you really think you'd be able to collect that reward if you and I got in a scrap over this? There will be other scams for you to pull, but today, you're a hero."
// Answer Text :
"P874757730" "You're right, there will be other scams."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3105577213" "Your contacts on the street are usually pretty reliable, they've learned not to pass you bad information. It sounds like the Tsoo are trying to make a major power play in order to fund their Rage production and flood Superadyne right off the streets as the thug drug of choice. If history is any indication, the first request for a ransom will be accompanied by a piece of the loved ones being held for ransom. You'd rather not see that happen, so best to collect the reward money on the down low now, that way the Tsoo don't get to cut a piece off of anyone."
// AcceptString :
"P3567444111" "Rescue the kidnapped family and claim the reward money"
// SendOffString :
"P1651900812" "According to the info you got, the Tsoo have the family members locked up tight in one of their Rage production facilities; one of the countless warehouse complexes in Paragon City. Since the ransom demand hasn't been sent yet, you imagine they'll be pretty surprised to have you knocking and kicking down their front door."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2224864169" "Rescue the kidnapped family"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1502621243" "The second the Tsoo send out their ransom demand every hero in the city is going to be on the Tsoo like stink on Dr. Vahzilok. Every moment you waste that reward money is less and less likely to be collected by you, and more and more likely to stay in some billionaire's bank account because of some hero's good sumaritan ideals."
// TaskTitle :
"P787750388" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Loose Lips Sink Ships</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4174929439" "The stench of the drug, Rage, being cooked hits you as you enter the building. But more alarming than that is the dead calm surrounding the building, telling you that the people in this neighborhood know better than to even look at the place,  let alone come around snooping."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2055913042" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Loose Lips Sink Ships</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The money was as good as yours and then that hot head Blast Furnace had to show up and ruin everything by 'coming to the rescue' with the fuzz. If you'd beat him down then and there you'd never have been able to collect that reward money, not without ransoming the Vanderton family off yourself. That just isn't your style anymore. On the plus side you did sneak off with a small fortune from Burning Fist's safe full of ill gotten gains. But most importantly, you made a good impression on the heirs to the Vanderton family fortune. Pride is a small price for you to pay to ensure you have a retirement plan in place."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1901611552" "Rescue Mrs. Vanderton"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1413328548" "Rescue Robert Vanderton"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P2280418312" "Rescue Mikaela Vanderton"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P639358051" "Mrs. Vanderton"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2591483279" "Please, let my children go. He'll pay you all the money for me, just don't hurt my children!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P679235232" "I'm saved! It's... Ummm... I don't recognize your costume..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P154143672" "Sorcerer"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1460674374" "Silence you yapping dog! We shall do as we wish, and you shall be silent or we'll cut out your tongue and send that to your husband!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P4080554135" "{HeroName}... So, you've come to steal our prize! Well all you'll get is DEATH!"
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P3239848900" "<shout>We have intruders!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P2045339674" "My husband will reward you greatly! Tell me you know where my children are being kept."

